    <section id="collaborate">
        <div class="collaboration-content">
            <p>SuperSonic is supported by several Indian Businesses, however, we look forward towards further collaboration. Under this collaboration,</p>
            <p>We are open to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Logo Branding on Car, Jersey, and Pit Display</li>
                <li>Acknowledgement on social media handles, portfolios, and verbal presentations</li>
                <li>Regular acknowledgment and recognition of sponsors in team communications, and press releases</li>
                <li>We expect to have a vision for a long-term partnership beyond a single competition cycle</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We are not obliged to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Keep our collaboration confidential</li>
                <li>Bound ourselves to a definite number of sponsors</li>
                <li>Continue the collaboration unwillingly</li>
            </ul>
